T1  - The Effect of SOX Section 404: Costs, Earnings Quality, and Stock Prices
AU  - ILIEV, PETER
Y1  - 2010/06/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/06/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.2010.01564.x
